[{"title":"LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps","url":"/2021/04/28/LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1824-Minimum-Sideway-Jumps\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps\"></a>LeetCode 1824. Minimum Sideway Jumps</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-sideway-jumps/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-sideway-jumps/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題首先要定義好dp[i][j]，在此我定義為老套路<br>dp[i][j]: minimum sideway jumps to point j at lane i</p>\n<p>之後推出狀態轉移方程:<br>if obstacles[j] == i + 1 then dp[i][j] = INT_MAX(如果當前路上有障礙則無法到達)<br>else dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j] (從上一個point直接過來)</p>\n<p>注意如果只寫到這邊的話，障礙後面的dp值會被設為INT_MAX，然而這是錯誤的，因為那個點的值有可能可以被該point的其他lane更新(從同個點的不同lane跳過來)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">minSideJumps</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; obstacles)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = obstacles.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() - <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&gt; <span class=\"built_in\">dp</span>(<span class=\"number\">3</span>, vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;(n+<span class=\"number\">1</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">0</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">1</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">2</span>][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; j &lt; n + <span class=\"number\">1</span>; j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> o = obstacles[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cur_min = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i + <span class=\"number\">1</span> == o)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[i][j] = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[i][j] = dp[i][j<span class=\"number\">-1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_min = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(cur_min, dp[i][j]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; k &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; k++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(k + <span class=\"number\">1</span> != o &amp;&amp; dp[k][j] &gt; cur_min)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dp[k][j] = cur_min + <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> ans = INT_MAX;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">3</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(ans, dp[i][n]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["Dynamic Programming"]},{"title":"LeetCode 45. Jump Game II","url":"/2021/05/06/LeetCode-45-Jump-Game-II/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-45-Jump-Game-II\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-45-Jump-Game-II\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 45. Jump Game II\"></a>LeetCode 45. Jump Game II</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/jump-game-ii/submissions/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/jump-game-ii/submissions/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>有一點進步的感覺囉</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題抱著感覺就是用DP去解的精神，老套路弄一弄就解出來了哈哈<br>首先定義dp[i]為老套路: minimum number of jumps at index i<br>之後對於每個點，遍歷它能走到的那些點，對那些點更新最小值(當前的dp值+1或是原本的dp值)即可</p>\n<p>另外這邊有BFS的解法，也挺有意思的應該會比DP快些<br><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/jump-game-ii/discuss/18019/10-lines-C%2B%2B-(16ms)-Python-BFS-Solutions-with-Explanations\">https://leetcode.com/problems/jump-game-ii/discuss/18019/10-lines-C%2B%2B-(16ms)-Python-BFS-Solutions-with-Explanations</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">jump</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">dp</span><span class=\"params\">(n, INT_MAX)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[<span class=\"number\">0</span>] = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len = nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i + j &lt; n &amp;&amp; j &lt;= len; j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                dp[i + j] = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(dp[i + j], dp[i] + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> dp[n<span class=\"number\">-1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["Dynamic Programming","Breadth First Search","May LeetCoding Challenge 2021"]},{"title":"LeetCode 1480. Running Sum of 1d Array","url":"/2021/05/04/LeetCode-1480-Running-Sum-of-1d-Array/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1480-Running-Sum-of-1d-Array\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1480-Running-Sum-of-1d-Array\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1480. Running Sum of 1d Array\"></a>LeetCode 1480. Running Sum of 1d Array</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/running-sum-of-1d-array/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/running-sum-of-1d-array/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>連續兩天hard後easy一下~</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">runningSum</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">ans</span><span class=\"params\">(n)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            cur += nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans[i] = cur;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["May LeetCoding Challenge 2021"]},{"title":"LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element","url":"/2021/04/27/LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1838-Frequency-of-the-Most-Frequent-Element\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element\"></a>LeetCode 1838. Frequency of the Most Frequent Element</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/frequency-of-the-most-frequent-element/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/frequency-of-the-most-frequent-element/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題的關鍵點在於如何快速地判斷全部的元素(區間內)變為x所需要的cost是否大於k。知道這點後，透過前處理(prefix sum和sort)，就能使用sliding window的技巧解題了。</p>\n<p>可惜比賽的時候就是想不到阿，sliding window的題目要回去多做做了…</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">maxFrequency</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">sort</span>(nums.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), nums.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>());</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ll j = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, sum = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, ans = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            sum += nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 當[j, i]的元素都變成nums[i]所需的cost大於k的時候，左側窗口縮小。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(nums[i] * (i - j + <span class=\"number\">1</span>) - sum &gt; k)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                sum -= nums[j];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            ans = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(ans, i - j + <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["Siding Window"]},{"title":"LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU","url":"/2021/04/25/LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-1834-Single-Threaded-CPU\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU\"></a>LeetCode 1834. Single-Threaded CPU</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/single-threaded-cpu/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/single-threaded-cpu/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>priority_queue(min heap)宣告方式<span id=\"more\"></span></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>根據題意我們需要照enqueue time大小依序執行task，這裡我們很自然地會希望任務以enqueue time的時間有小到大排序，但因為返回的結果是task原本的index，所以需要前處理不然順序會亂掉。</p>\n<p>在這裡因為任務處理的順序已經固定了，所以在最外面的while循環(確認ans是否已將task都處理了)裡面，會先決定以當前的時間有哪些task能加入到avalible tasks(priority_queue)裡。</p>\n<p>最後的部分則是一次處理一個task，如果avalible tasks裡面沒有task了，則cur_time變成當前idx指向的task的起始時間。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> ll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">typedef</span> pair&lt;ll, ll&gt; pll;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; <span class=\"title\">getOrder</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; tasks)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        priority_queue&lt;pll, vector&lt;pll&gt;, greater&lt;pll&gt;&gt; pq;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tasks[i].<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">sort</span>(tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), tasks.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>());</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">        vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ll cur_time = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, idx = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(ans.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() != n)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(idx &lt; n &amp;&amp; tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">0</span>] &lt;= cur_time)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                pq.<span class=\"built_in\">push</span>(&#123;tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">1</span>], tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">2</span>]&#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                idx++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(pq.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> cur_task = pq.<span class=\"built_in\">top</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                pq.<span class=\"built_in\">pop</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                ans.<span class=\"built_in\">push_back</span>(cur_task.second);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_time += cur_task.first;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur_time = tasks[idx][<span class=\"number\">0</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["Heap"]},{"title":"LeetCode 665. Non-decreasing Array","url":"/2021/05/05/LeetCode-665-Non-decreasing-Array/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-665-Non-decreasing-Array\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-665-Non-decreasing-Array\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 665. Non-decreasing Array\"></a>LeetCode 665. Non-decreasing Array</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/non-decreasing-array/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/non-decreasing-array/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>期中結束刷題紓壓囉</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題可以先簡化只有為三個值的話要怎麼判斷<br>可以分為兩個case，示意圖可以參考下面解法的評論區，這邊格式會跑掉就不弄了QQ<br><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/non-decreasing-array/discuss/106826/JavaC%2B%2B-Simple-greedy-like-solution-with-explanation\">https://leetcode.com/problems/non-decreasing-array/discuss/106826/JavaC%2B%2B-Simple-greedy-like-solution-with-explanation</a></p>\n<p>基本上要嘛你就是改小，不然就是改大(廢話<br>不過這裡greedy的思想就是你可以的話就改小，這樣才比較不會影響後面的人嘛(題目限制只能改一個值)<br>Case 1: 這裡可以很輕易的把nums[i]小，也就是改成下一個值nums[i+1]以滿足non-decreasing<br>Case 2: 這裡不能直接改小，因為nums[i-1] &gt; nums[i+1]，所以要改大，讓nums[i+1] = nums[i]</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> <span class=\"title\">checkPossibility</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cnt = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; nums.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>() - <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[i] &gt; nums[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// 注意等號</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(i == <span class=\"number\">0</span> || nums[i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] &lt;= nums[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    nums[i] = nums[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    nums[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = nums[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cnt++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(cnt &gt;= <span class=\"number\">2</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["May LeetCoding Challenge 2021","Greedy"]},{"title":"LeetCode 630. Course Schedule III","url":"/2021/05/03/LeetCode-630-Course-Schedule-III/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-630-Course-Schedule-III\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-630-Course-Schedule-III\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 630. Course Schedule III\"></a>LeetCode 630. Course Schedule III</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/course-schedule-iii/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/course-schedule-iii/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>又是一題想不到貪心策略的greedy題冏</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>這題很直覺的以ending time做排序，因為結束時間越前面的先處理比較不會影響到後面的，蠻合理的嘛(?，然後就是重要的貪心策略！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>當前的課程加進去後，如果全部課程的完成時間，大於目前課程的結束時間，則把pq裡最長的課程換成當前的課程</li>\n</ul>\n<p>這樣能保證課程數量不虧(+1後-1)，而且能使總體完成時間縮短！</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">bool</span> <span class=\"title\">cmp</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; a, vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&amp; b)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> a[<span class=\"number\">1</span>] &lt; b[<span class=\"number\">1</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">scheduleCourse</span><span class=\"params\">(vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; courses)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">sort</span>(courses.<span class=\"built_in\">begin</span>(), courses.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>(), cmp);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        priority_queue&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; pq;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> cur = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; courses.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>(); i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            cur += courses[i][<span class=\"number\">0</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            pq.<span class=\"built_in\">push</span>(courses[i][<span class=\"number\">0</span>]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(cur &gt; courses[i][<span class=\"number\">1</span>])&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                cur -= pq.<span class=\"built_in\">top</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                pq.<span class=\"built_in\">pop</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> pq.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["May LeetCoding Challenge 2021","Heap","Greedy"]},{"title":"LeetCode 745. Prefix and Suffix Search","url":"/2021/05/02/LeetCode-745-Prefix-and-Suffix-Search/","content":"<h3 id=\"LeetCode-745-Prefix-and-Suffix-Search\"><a href=\"#LeetCode-745-Prefix-and-Suffix-Search\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LeetCode 745. Prefix and Suffix Search\"></a>LeetCode 745. Prefix and Suffix Search</h3><blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/prefix-and-suffix-search/\">https://leetcode.com/problems/prefix-and-suffix-search/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>重新回歸每日任務，在此紀錄期許自己能完成五月的挑戰！<br>上個月休息沒有繼續堅持的下場就是積分直直落QQ，果然還是要每天練習當作醒腦體操跟維持手感啊！</p>\n<p>第一天就是hard題真是令人格外興奮(?<br>雖然標記為Trie這個標籤，但這個主題我還不太熟(cp值太低)所以就先跳過這個方法哈哈<br>這裡主要用花花的解法: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a-4WbFqalIA\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a-4WbFqalIA</a><br>不過因為題目限制有變動所以也稍微修改了一下code</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<p>如果想要query的時間加速，那自然想到的有map O(1)的方法，雖然我沒想到…<br>為了能同時查看word是否有包含prefix跟suffix，所以我們直接把這兩個用 “_” 串起來當作map的key<br>做完後查詢就很方便了，雖然產生的key很多(SC很高)不過整體下來速度也不慢。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">WordFilter</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">WordFilter</span>(vector&lt;string&gt;&amp; words) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> idx = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">auto</span>&amp; word: words)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n = word.<span class=\"built_in\">size</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;string&gt; <span class=\"title\">prefixes</span><span class=\"params\">(n + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"function\">vector&lt;string&gt; <span class=\"title\">suffixes</span><span class=\"params\">(n + <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                prefixes[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = prefixes[i] + word[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">                suffixes[i+<span class=\"number\">1</span>] = word[n-i<span class=\"number\">-1</span>] + suffixes[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; j &lt;= n; j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    dic_[prefixes[i] + <span class=\"string\">&quot;_&quot;</span> + suffixes[j]] = idx;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            idx++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">f</span><span class=\"params\">(string prefix, string suffix)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        string key = prefix + <span class=\"string\">&quot;_&quot;</span> + suffix;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">auto</span> it = dic_.<span class=\"built_in\">find</span>(key);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(it != dic_.<span class=\"built_in\">end</span>()) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> it-&gt;second;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">-1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">private</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    unordered_map&lt;string, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&gt; dic_;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","categories":["LeetCode"],"tags":["May LeetCoding Challenge 2021","HashMap","Trie"]},{"title":"hexo common commands","url":"/2021/04/24/hexo-common-commands/","content":"<h3 id=\"Common-Deploy-command\"><a href=\"#Common-Deploy-command\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Common Deploy command\"></a>Common Deploy command</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>","categories":["Hexo"],"tags":["Hexo"]}]